Effective Date: February 1, 2024
At Plaid, we understand the importance of privacy and transparency. The purpose of this Candidate Privacy Notice (“Notice”) is to explain how Plaid Inc. and its subsidiaries, including Plaid Financial Ltd. and Plaid, B.V. (collectively, “Plaid”, “we”, “our”, or “us”), collect, use, and share personal data and information from and about potential candidates (“you” or “your”) for positions with Plaid (“Candidate Information”).
Please note that if you submit your CV/resume or other Candidate Information through our website, we may also collect and process information about you in connection with your access to or use of Plaid’s website. Additional information regarding our use of your data can be found in our Privacy Statement. Further information about the types of cookies we use on our website, why we use them, and how you can control or limit the use of cookies can be found in our
Cookie Policy
.
