Nederland - Privacyverklaring
Effective Date: February 22, 2024
Thank you for using Plaid! We hope you will take some time to read this Privacy Statement carefully.
This Privacy Statement explains the ways Plaid Inc. and its subsidiaries, including Plaid Financial Ltd., Plaid Consumer Reporting Agency, Inc., and Plaid, B.V., (collectively, “Plaid”, “we”, “our”, and “us”) collect, use, and share information about you (ie. the developer, customer, website visitor) when you visit or use Plaid’s websites, or incorporate our products and services into your software application , or otherwise interact with us (for example, when you make a customer service inquiry or attend a Plaid event or webinar). This Privacy Statement does not apply to information we collect about end users when they connect their financial accounts to an app through Plaid, or to the data used to create a Plaid CRA consumer report. If you’re looking for information as to how we handle data collected under those circumstances, please see our
End User Privacy Policy
or
Plaid Consumer Reporting Agency Privacy Policy
.
