Privacy Notice (Website and Mobile App)
Preamble
When you visit and use Sumsub websites, we collect and process certain information about your interactions with the website and the data you leave at your sole discretion. For more information, please read this Privacy Notice attentively.
This is the Privacy Notice of the Sumsub group of companies: Sum and Substance Ltd., incorporated and registered in England with company number 09688671 (hereinafter – Sumsub or we) together with all affiliated companies and trading divisions, irrespective of location or jurisdiction. More information about our group can be found in
Provision 14
of this Privacy Notice.
